snippet.title: urban lockdown
snippet.description:
Plot: a crazed crime boss is finally captured and imprisoned due to the testimony of a woman he tried to assault. He orchestrates his revenge and enables all prisoners to work together and break out and take over city. As he sends his not so loyal right hand man to deliver the woman there is one man entering town who can put an end to all of it...her brother !

Written, edited and directed by Andrew Thatcher

and check out my production site for info on the official video game

www.thatcherproductions.org
